text: Sehdev or Sahdava collectively ascertained from _Sadhiora_ is an Indian caste found among the Kshatriya of Mair rajput.It is classified as (Upper class) and Warrior, and back in the predated era this surname hold stronghold meaningful praising which denominate an Immortalised human being empowering themselves equal to god. == See also == * Kshatriya == References == Category:Castes
title: Sehdev (caste)
